RE-HYPOTHECATION
HAS LOST HUNDREDS OF
FARMERS THOUSANDS
OF DOLLARS THAT WERE
SITTING IN THEIR
MF GLOBAL ACCOUNTS
LET US NOW SHED
A SMALL LIGHT ON THE
RE-HYPOTHECATORS
MONSTERS THAT FEED
OFF THE WEALTH OF
OTHERS
RN OFF THE LIG
ORE WOLF BLITIE
SEES US!
CAN SOMEONE
TELL JON COR乙INE
AND JAMIE DIMON
TO GET OFF OF MY
FACE!
THANK GOD
NOW WE CAN
DESTROY THE
WORLD ECONOMY
IN PEACE
